{"tid":2331490,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"路透社：特朗普簽署一項《外國公司問責法》以收緊中國公司赴美上市嘅要求","createTime":"2020-12-18T22:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T22:01:12.000Z","uid":310867,"like":95,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5caedbc1e2609a582457059498f51fa9cee0141e","tid":2331490,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T22:28:34.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普簽署《外國公司問責法》（Holding Foreign Companies Accountable Act），中國公司如果要去美國上市，將面臨更嚴格的審計要求。<br />\n<br />\n美國參眾兩院分別在今年5月及12月通過《外國公司問責法》，要求外國公司來美國上市及交易，<span class=\"red\">需要提交詳盡的審計紀錄底稿，如果連續3年都沒有辦法達標，那麼便要退市。這項審計要求對赴美上市的中資公司帶來很大壓力，原因是中國法律規定，除非得到監管當局許可，否則不可將審計底稿交給境外人士及機構。</span><br />\n<br />\n美國認為《外國公司問責法》是保護投資者的重要措施，因為中國多家赴美的公司，例如瑞幸咖啡都涉嫌財務做假，因此有必要加強監管。不過，<span class=\"red\">中國就認為法案是針對中資公司，當中一些條款，例如要求披露公司董事的政黨背景，就被視為是要對付中共滲透。</span><br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201219/ERIXJ35YO5FHXA4JTOO5DH4MQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201219%2FERIXJ35YO5FHXA4JTOO5DH4MQE%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBTizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=69f5dbea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201219%2FERIXJ35YO5FHXA4JTOO5DH4MQE%2F&h=6fa548c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201219/ERIXJ35YO5FHXA4JTOO5DH4MQE/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">&quot;The Holding Foreign Companies Accountable Act&quot; bars securities of foreign companies from being listed on any U.S. exchange if they have failed to comply with the U.S. Public Accounting Oversight Board's audits for three years in a row.</span><br />\n<br />\nWhile it applies to companies from any country, the legislation's sponsors intended it to target Chinese companies listed in the United States, <span class=\"red\">such as Alibaba (BABA.K), tech firm Pinduoduo Inc and oil giant PetroChina Co Ltd.</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.reuters.com/article/amp/idUSKBN28S2ZJ?__twitter_impression=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Famp%2FidUSKBN28S2ZJ%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBTizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=d54997f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Famp%2FidUSKBN28S2ZJ%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&h=e739f129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.reuters.com/article/amp/idUSKBN28S2ZJ?__twitter_impression=true</a>"},{"pid":"328a62cf8f84b275d5b799f80d74f6c528a4a659","tid":2331490,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T22:29:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e16e6945161bbf83764622039a279e95fdc694aa","tid":2331490,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T22:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c3622535b3c0467f66c7bc0e5c69e707177f3d","tid":2331490,"uid":158888,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T22:53:54.000Z","msg":"拜登上場即刻再賣國"},{"pid":"568c0ea824b74bb4d7b8d9dd85bd1d3b0ef549a8","tid":2331490,"uid":3553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T22:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0067407b7ab8d8fdc3a43a6aa7ab4eae03a6e807","tid":2331490,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T22:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f2c7716053397426e248c7704c671bb91afb2a","tid":2331490,"uid":70487,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T22:59:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">共和黨籍參議員克魯茲（Ted Cruz）提出反對，直指法案不是為了香港制定，而是為了民主黨自己而制定；他並指控民主黨議員試圖利用香港危機，以達成他們長年希望修改美國移民法律的目標。<br />\n<br />\n克魯茲指出，在美國目前移民法律下，香港人本來就有資格成為難民，川普7月也特別增加難民名額，並將其分配給香港。他說，「香港人民自由和選擇法案」恐會大幅降低美國難民門檻，導致連無法舉證有被迫害可信恐懼的人士都能取得難民身分。<br />\n<br />\n他強調：「沒有理由降低這個標準，這麼做可能有遭致中共利用的風險，他們可能會送更多中國間諜到美國。」<br />\n<br />\n克魯茲也質疑，若民主黨真的有心要對中國強硬，就應該以「一致同意」方式通過他的「劇本法案」（SCRIPT Act），讓為了進入中國市場而更改電影內容的美國企業無法取得聯邦政府資金或資源，例如美國娛樂影視公司迪士尼（Disney）。<br />\n<br />\n布魯門塔當場提出反對，致使克魯茲的「劇本法案」連同「香港人民自由和選擇法案」今天雙雙闖關參議院失敗。</span>"},{"pid":"088922827b15b8f84c9da8a2fd9ffb5dc50a5e43","tid":2331490,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T23:24:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b09cc7937b9272f967d108f2b75ecead7ee94bd0","tid":2331490,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T00:18:04.000Z","msg":"蛋殼﹕nmsl"},{"pid":"940b03f362cf5ba49574c3a536e5df07b637a9db","tid":2331490,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5caedbc1e2609a582457059498f51fa9cee0141e","tid":2331490,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T22:28:34.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普簽署《外國公司問責法》（Holding Foreign Companies Accountable Act），中國公司如果要去美國上市，將面臨更嚴格的審計要求。<br />\n<br />\n美國參眾兩院分別在今年5月及12月通過《外國公司問責法》，要求外國公司來美國上市及交易，<span class=\"red\">需要提交詳盡的審計紀錄底稿，如果連續3年都沒有辦法達標，那麼便要退市。這項審計要求對赴美上市的中資公司帶來很大壓力，原因是中國法律規定，除非得到監管當局許可，否則不可將審計底稿交給境外人士及機構。</span><br />\n<br />\n美國認為《外國公司問責法》是保護投資者的重要措施，因為中國多家赴美的公司，例如瑞幸咖啡都涉嫌財務做假，因此有必要加強監管。不過，<span class=\"red\">中國就認為法案是針對中資公司，當中一些條款，例如要求披露公司董事的政黨背景，就被視為是要對付中共滲透。</span><br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201219/ERIXJ35YO5FHXA4JTOO5DH4MQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201219%2FERIXJ35YO5FHXA4JTOO5DH4MQE%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBTizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=69f5dbea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternationa